{"tid":472823,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我記得上堂講過  對日本人黎講 漢字書寫係難","createTime":"2017-11-18T15:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T04:02:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6839b800d018d2efa71ebb48941a0b84dffb2c94","tid":472823,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"我記得上堂講過 <br />\n對日本人黎講 漢字書寫係難 <br />\n但係用黎睇/閱讀係好方便 <br />\n日本青年只係唔識寫 <br />\n同埋而家電腦方便左漢字 佢地更加唔會寫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n響日本，係d死老野先鐘意寫漢字，後生仔不嬲唔鐘意寫<br />\n<br />\n對我嚟講，漢字識睇就夠，根本唔需要識寫"},{"pid":"b7b4a02d2b37085f3333cb475c88adbd55ba8e30","tid":472823,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b68d974e4158126cddc57311cb34cdd869f482","tid":472823,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"辛苦樓主"},{"pid":"ca157b72dc33b2c28b46aa75932d9ac042a12459","tid":472823,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}